import { Segment, Display } from './styles'
import { Context } from '../../context/Context'
import { useContext } from 'react'

function SegmentsDisplay() {
  const context = useContext(Context)
  console.log(context.apiNumber)

  return (
    <Display>
      <Segment className="B"></Segment>
      <Segment className="C"></Segment>
      <Segment className="D"></Segment>
      <Segment className="E"></Segment>
      <Segment className="F"></Segment>
      <Segment className="G"></Segment>
    </Display>
  )
}

export default SegmentsDisplay
